&lt;iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2o5k_BzJqsY?start=28244" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</content><category term="Videos"></category></entry><entry><title>Compilador - Analise léxica</title><link href="https://bugelseif.github.io/website/compilador-analise-lexica.html" rel="alternate"></link><published>2022-07-11T00:00:00-03:00</published><updated>2022-07-11T00:00:00-03:00</updated><author><name>Bruna Ferreira</name></author><id>tag:bugelseif.github.io,2022-07-11:/website/compilador-analise-lexica.html</id><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Uma atividade opcional da faculdade foi fazer um compilador, nessa live eu mostro os passos no analisador léxico e corrijo alguns erros que estavam sendo apresentados.&lt;/p&gt;
