&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/bugelseif/AtividadeBD" target="_blank"&gt;Acompanhe aqui!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="Projetos"></category><category term="Conteudo"></category><category term="SQL"></category><category term="pratica"></category></entry><entry><title>Caso de uso: RegEx</title><link href="https://bugelseif.github.io/website/caso-de-uso-regex.html" rel="alternate"></link><published>2021-12-16T00:00:00-03:00</published><updated>2021-12-16T00:00:00-03:00</updated><author><name>Bruna Ferreira</name></author><id>tag:bugelseif.github.io,2021-12-16:/website/caso-de-uso-regex.html</id><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Nesse artigo exemplifiquei, usando Python, algumas formas de escrever um RegEx para validar um mesmo padrão: CPF.&lt;/p&gt;
